citations:
    citation-asos-daenerys-i:
        source: source-asos
        properties:
            locator: "Daenerys I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Daenerys sailing from Qarth toward Pentos on Illyrio's ship Balerion, accompanied by Ser Jorah Mormont, Arstan Whitebeard (Strong Belwas's squire), and Strong Belwas. Discussion of Rhaegar's character. Ser Jorah kisses Daenerys unexpectedly. Jorah proposes diverting to Astapor to buy Unsullied slave soldiers."
